                    Specifies the first vector to be used in the comparison operation.
                </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies the second vector to be used in the comparison operation.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">equal</code> returns a boolean vector in which each element <span class="emphasis"><em>i</em></span> is computed
            as <em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em>[<span class="emphasis"><em>i</em></span>] == <em class="parameter"><code>y</code></em>[<span class="emphasis"><em>i</em></span>].
